<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>806</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ de xīn nǎ nǐ yào chēng sòng yé hé huá, bù kě wàng jì tā de yī qiè ēn huì.
 wǒ de xīn nǎ nǐ yào chēng sòng yé hé huá, shì tā tú mǒ wǒ suǒ yǒu de guò fàn.
 wǒ de jiǎo bù bèi tā suǒ lì dìng, wǒ de shēng mìng bèi tā zhǎng guǎn.
 tā duì wǒ de ài qiān gǔ bù biàn, tā zǒng shì cháng zài wǒ shēn biān.
 wǒ de xīn nǎ yào xiàng zhǔ gē chàng, gē chàng tā wǒ cí ài yǒng bù gǎi biàn.
 wǒ de xīn nǎ yào xiàng zhǔ gē chàng, wǒ yào tiān tiān jiàn tā de róng miàn.</lyrics>
<title>wǒ de xīn nǎ nǐ yào chēng sòng yé hé huá 迦南806</title>
</song>